./fusexmp pass /home/user/mirror/ /home/user/mount/

create:
touch sample.txt
cat sample.txt

read:
cat sample.txt

write:
echo "sample text message" > sample.txt

fusermount -u /home/user/mount


/home/user/mirror is the folder that is mirrored, can r/w decrypted but cannot r/w encrypted
/home/user/mount is the mountpoint, can r/w decrypted and encrypted